	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />All PRG RAM can be save ram. (A battery will store the contents of RAM while it's off)<br /><br />(All CHR RAM could be too, but only <a href="http://bootgod.dyndns.org:7777/profile.php?id=2696" class="postlink">one cartridge</a> does that)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
